  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ah, just the person I wanted to see! #p511# of #m10004000# has requested a special weapon for the warriors of the town. But there’s no way I can finish the order alone in time. Would you lend this old craftsman a hand?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Much obliged! What I need are #b#t4003000#s#k. Hunt down #r#o15#s#k around #m10004000#, gather the materials, and craft 10 for me. Why something so simple, you ask? Hah! You’re not giving them nearly enough credit!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Hmph… an apprentice turning down his master… Back in my day, we wouldn’t even dream of such a thing."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Wonderful! Just what I needed. You really are a reliable apprentice—strong arms and a good heart, too!"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Here, take this #t2002005#. Think of it as a little boost to help sharpen your weaponcrafting skills."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Though… this might be a problem. I feel like #p511# will keep sending requests like this my way. Looks like I’ll be relying on you more often, eh? Don’t wander too far!"
        }
      },
